OL,3,CFather and son spared jail for selling
OL,4,Cperegrine falcons in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"The sale of peregrine falcons has
OL,7,Fbecome an extremely lucrative business
OL,8,Fand Timothy and Lewis Hall took
OL,9,Fadvantage of that for their own
OL,10,Ffinancial gain and to the detriment of
OL,11,Fthe wild peregrine falcon population
OL,12,Fin the South of Scotland.
OL,14,F"Their illegal activities had the
OL,15,Fpotential to have a devastating impact
OL,16,Fon the entire population of nesting
OL,17,Fperegrine falcons in that part of the
OL,18,Fcountry.
