OL,6,F"If their illegal activities had
OL,7,Fcontinued unchallenged, this would
OL,8,Fhave had a massive impact on the
OL,9,Fpopulation of young birds, and had the
OL,10,Fpotential to wipe out the entire
OL,11,Fpopulation of peregrine falcons in the
OL,13,F"This case has been a monumental
OL,14,Feffort by Detective Constable Steven
OL,15,FIrvine who led the investigation and
OL,16,Fwas determined to bring the
OL,17,Fperpetrators to justice, going into
OL,18,Fmeticulous detail to unravel the true
OL,19,Fextent of the criminality involved.
